## Features Overview

### Messages
- Daily love messages
- Random compliments
- Romantic poems
- Morning and night greetings

### ASCII Art
- Heart designs
- Love banners
- Name art displays

### Love Calculator
- Days together calculator
- Love percentage calculator

### Romantic Utilities
- Love reminders
- Custom love note generator

